text: Stevan Milošević (born 13 October 1985) is a Montenegrin professional basketball player who last played for Union Olimpija of the Slovenian League.Olimpija inks veteran center Milosevic He is a 2.11 m tall center. ==References== ==External links== * Eurobasket.com profile * FIBA Profile Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:ABA League players Category:AEL Limassol (basketball) players Category:BC Nizhny Novgorod players Category:Centers (basketball) Category:JDA Dijon Basket players Category:KK Budućnost players Category:KK Crvena zvezda players Category:KK Mornar Bar players Category:KK Olimpija players Category:KK Partizan players Category:Köln 99ers players Category:Montenegrin expatriate basketball people in Serbia Category:Montenegrin men's basketball players Category:Trabzonspor B.K. players
